data.description: Welcome to this cozy 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home. Inside, you'll find a freshly painted interior that creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere.  The home comes with new floors and carpet, adding a touch of beauty. Each room has ceiling fans, ensuring a comfortable atmosphere throughout the year. Additionally, window air conditioners in every room allow for personalized climate control. The interior flows seamlessly from room to room, offering an open, airy feel.  Outside, you'll discover a nice-sized yard, suitable for gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the outdoors. The property also has the potential for an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU), providing flexibility for extended family, guests, or rental income.   Whether you're a first-time buyer or an investor, this home is a practical choice. Its convenient location and well-maintained features make it an appealing option for those seeking comfort and value. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this house your home.
